Company Overview
JAC Recruitment is an International Recruitment Agency, having its first business in the UK and expanding to other regions. As part of the TAZAKI Group, currently JAC Recruitment operates in 10 countries with 22 offices. JAC Recruitment Indonesia has been operating since 2002 and currently has 3 branches in Bekasi, Karawang, and Surabaya. Together with more than 70 consultants, we constantly aim to support each and every Client with the right people for the right position. On behalf one of our clients, a big palm of refinery located in East Java, we are looking for IT Manager. He will be responsible for developing and improving IT system.
